## Backend API base URL — set to your Render backend after deploy
## Local:      http://localhost:5000
## Production: https://sanrachna-backend.onrender.com
VITE_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:5000

## Planning / Report Engine API base — set to your Render report-engine after deploy
## Local:      http://localhost:8001
## Production: https://sanrachna-report-engine.onrender.com
VITE_PLANNING_API_BASE=http://localhost:8001
